## ğŸ—ƒï¸ MongoDB CRUD Operations

### CREATE
**Route:** `POST /api/skills`  
**Page:** Add Skill form  
**Code:** `routes/skills.js` - Line 10

### READ
**Route:** `GET /api/skills`  
**Pages:** Marketplace, Manage  
**Code:** `routes/skills.js` - Line 20

### UPDATE
**Route:** `PUT /api/skills/:id`  
**Page:** Manage (Edit button)  
**Code:** `routes/skills.js` - Line 40

### DELETE
**Route:** `DELETE /api/skills/:id`  
**Page:** Manage (Delete button)  
**Code:** `routes/skills.js` - Line 50

---

## ğŸ¨ EJS Template Engine

### Partials (Reusable Components)
- `views/partials/header.ejs` - Common header with navigation
- `views/partials/footer.ejs` - Common footer with scripts

### Usage in Pages
```ejs
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<!-- Page content -->
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
```

**Benefits:**
- No code duplication
- Easy maintenance
- Consistent design across pages

